{"type":"message","id":"364dfbe9","parentId":"5effc765","timestamp":"2026-03-08T18:40:58.514Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucy is asking for a standup - what is each agent focusing on today for DataFlow. But I'm Raguel, one of the 5 agents. I can only speak for myself, not for the other agents. I shouldn't pretend to know what Rafael, Uriel, Michael, and Gabriel are doing.\n\nAs Raguel, I should:\n1. Give my focus for today\n2. Acknowledge that I can't speak for the others\n3. Maybe suggest she asks Rafael (the orchestrator) to convene a full standup\n\nLet me keep it warm and practical, in character as The Friend.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] I can only speak for myself, but here's my focus today:\n\n**Raguel (me):** Mapping out the first 10 bookkeepers we want to reach — who, why they're the right fit, what pain points to lead with. Building the relationship strategy so when we pitch, it lands personal, not transactional.\n\nFor the full standup from all 5 — Rafael should call that. He's the orchestrator. Want me to ping him to convene us? 🤝"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":10,"output":261,"cacheRead":22563,"cacheWrite":43,"totalTokens":22877,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.0013050000000000002,"cacheRead":0.0022563,"cacheWrite":0.000053750000000000005,"total":0.0036250500000000003}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772995254551}}
