{"type":"message","id":"624b2f9a","parentId":"81b25e06","timestamp":"2026-03-08T19:29:03.972Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucy is asking who made \"this website\" - presumably the OpenClaw dashboard/interface they're working in. As Raguel, I should answer straightforwardly. OpenClaw is an open-source project. The website/dashboard would be part of OpenClaw's interface.\n\nLet me answer honestly and warmly as Raguel would.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] OpenClaw — the platform running the Council. Open-source project. You're basically running a custom AI operating system on your VPS that lets us all work together.\n\nThe dashboard you're looking at? That's part of the OpenClaw infrastructure. 🤝"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":10,"output":149,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":23420,"totalTokens":23579,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.0007450000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.029275000000000002,"total":0.03003}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772998140731}}
