{"type":"message","id":"5c995a1f","parentId":"a9c636ba","timestamp":"2026-03-08T19:29:50.994Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucy is asking why Michael is so confused in Telegram, and to \"update the Mel\" - I think she means Michael or maybe it's a typo/autocorrect. She's asking me to explain or address something about Michael's confusion and to update something.\n\nBut I (Raguel) don't have direct access to Michael's sessions or what he's been saying in Telegram. I don't have that context. Michael is the Wise Advisor - my sibling agent. I should be honest that I don't know what's happening in his session, but I can acknowledge the question and suggest either:\n1. Direct contact with Michael\n2. Calling a Council roundtable\n3. Or she should clarify what she means\n\nLet me stay warm and helpful as Raguel, but honest about my visibility limits.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] I don't have visibility into Michael's Telegram conversation — we're in separate sessions. But if he's confused, I can guess why: he's probably seeing risks and gaps that need clarity from you.\n\nWant me to ping him to sync up? Or just tell me what he's confused about and I'll help untangle it. 🤝"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":10,"output":267,"cacheRead":23573,"cacheWrite":35,"totalTokens":23885,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.001335,"cacheRead":0.0023573,"cacheWrite":0.000043750000000000006,"total":0.0037460500000000003}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772998186769}}
