{"type":"message","id":"0cc35407","parentId":"80cb8d07","timestamp":"2026-03-09T02:11:50.519Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucy is asking why Rafael is wearing the Shield icon. But Rafael is The Guide (🧭) and Michael is The Wise Advisor (🛡️). The shield is Michael's emoji, not Rafael's.\n\nLucy might be confused about which agent is which. As Raguel, I should gently clarify - Rafael should have the compass (🧭), not the shield. Michael has the shield (🛡️).\n\nThis could also be a testing/checking message where Lucy is seeing if I'm paying attention and know who's who.\n\nLet me respond clearly and warmly, correcting this gently.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Rafael has the compass (🧭) — he's The Guide.\n\nThe shield (🛡️) is Michael's — he's The Wise Advisor, the protector, the one who sees risks.\n\nYou might be seeing Michael's icon somewhere? 🤝"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":10,"output":211,"cacheRead":24171,"cacheWrite":32,"totalTokens":24424,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.0010550000000000002,"cacheRead":0.0024171,"cacheWrite":0.00004,"total":0.0035221000000000002}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773022307071}}
