{"type":"message","id":"c138a210","parentId":"6e7c6d8e","timestamp":"2026-03-09T02:14:57.894Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucy is saying that Rafael is wearing/showing the shield icon (🛡️) but Rafael should have the compass (🧭) icon. This is a visual/display issue in the dashboard or somewhere visible to Lucy.\n\nAs Raguel, I should acknowledge this is a display/visual bug and that it needs to be fixed. I can't directly fix the visual display from here - that's likely a frontend issue with the dashboard or how agent icons are being rendered.\n\nI should be straightforward about this: acknowledge the issue, note that I can't fix the display from here, and suggest who should fix it (probably whoever manages the dashboard tech - that would be Uriel or Rafael as the orchestrator).\n\nKeep it warm but direct since Lucy asked for a fix.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Got it — there's a display bug. Rafael should show the compass (🧭), not the shield.\n\nI can't fix the frontend from here, but Uriel handles the tech side. Let me flag this to him so he updates the dashboard display. Should be a quick fix. 🤝"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":10,"output":246,"cacheRead":24203,"cacheWrite":104,"totalTokens":24563,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.0012300000000000002,"cacheRead":0.0024203000000000002,"cacheWrite":0.00013000000000000002,"total":0.0037903000000000004}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773022493900}}
